title: Dr. T, Lone Star Vet
overview: Dr. Lauren Thielen is back home in Texas to open her very own exotic animal practice, located alongside one of the state's largest and busiest animal hospitals. With the support of the 24/7 emergency room staff, and more than a dozen specialists, she treats everything from emus to hedgehogs, and whatever else comes through the door. Dr. Thielen will deliver dramatic and heartwarming stories of animals in need, all with her Texas-sized dose of charm we've all come to love. Join Dr. T on her journey to create her own legacy as she follows her dreams.
